Author: prettypinkneversweet
Text: All black and a nice black bootie is ultra slimming! Not to mention chic af. Throw in a pop of color in like your purse or hair accessories. Maybe red for the holidays. Sparky red❤️

Author: Ednosonline
Text: You can also achieve that confidence with great hair, accessories and a flattering outfit :) Logically, you can't lose a big amount of weight in that Times anyways. Maybe try to eat slightly more in the week before to make sure you dont binge, and then do some kind of Short fast on the day before, to get the feeling of being Slim and empty?
